high_descs: Turn to the right then left and go forward to the desk.
Pick up the pencil from the desk.
Step to the right and go to the other desk.
Place the pencil on top of the desk.
anns.task_desc: Move a pencil to a different desk.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go across the room to the small desk across from you.
Pick up the pencil in front of the lamp, on the small desk.
Move over to the far, left end of the large desk.
Place the pencil on the large desk, to the right of the laptop.
anns.task_desc: Put a pencil on the large desk.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the middle of the room then turn left and walk to the desk.
Pick up the yellow pencil from in front of the white lamp.
Turn right and walk to the map then turn left to face the desk.
Put the pencil on the desk next to the right side of the laptop.
anns.task_desc: Put a pencil next to a laptop.
